### TIDO — API test requests
### Requires the "REST Client" VS Code extension (humao.rest-client).
### Start the server first (F5, or `go run .`), then click "Send Request"
### above any block below. Each one is independent.

@host = http://localhost:8080

### 1. Home page renders
GET {{host}}/

### 2. Static assets are served (should be 200, not 404)
GET {{host}}/static/css/style.css

### 3. Documents are served
GET {{host}}/documents/TIDO-Constitution.pdf

### 4. Contact form — VALID submission
# Expect: 200, HTML fragment containing "form-status show success"
# and "Thank you, Jane!"
POST {{host}}/api/contact
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

name=Jane Doe&email=jane@example.com&phone=0712345678&subject=Volunteering&message=I would like to volunteer with TIDO next month.

### 5. Contact form — INVALID: all required fields empty
# Expect: 200, HTML fragment with 4 field-level errors (name, email,
# subject, message) and the "Please correct the highlighted fields" banner
POST {{host}}/api/contact
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

name=&email=&phone=&subject=&message=

### 6. Contact form — INVALID: bad email format
# Expect: error on the email field only (others valid)
POST {{host}}/api/contact
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

name=Jane Doe&email=not-an-email&phone=&subject=Hello&message=This message is long enough.

### 7. Contact form — INVALID: message too short (<10 chars)
# Expect: error on the message field only
POST {{host}}/api/contact
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

name=Jane Doe&email=jane@example.com&phone=&subject=Hello&message=short

### 8. Contact form — INVALID: malformed phone (when provided)
# Expect: error on the phone field only — phone is optional, but if
# present must look like a phone number
POST {{host}}/api/contact
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

name=Jane Doe&email=jane@example.com&phone=abc&subject=Hello&message=This message is long enough.

### 9. Reset the contact form (used by the "Send Another Message" button)
# Expect: a blank form partial, no values, no errors
GET {{host}}/api/contact/reset

### 10. Newsletter — VALID email
# Expect: "Subscribed! Thank you for staying connected with TIDO."
POST {{host}}/api/newsletter
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

email=fan@example.com

### 11. Newsletter — INVALID email
# Expect: re-rendered form + "Please enter a valid email address."
POST {{host}}/api/newsletter
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

email=not-an-email
